{"tid":1943852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"加拿大家長你地可以幫翻啲真係有需要嘅人呢？","createTime":"2020-03-26T04:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T15:10:07.000Z","uid":58799,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e82dc993144f05294a91d55c6609956d9de23a6","tid":1943852,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:24:30.000Z","msg":"我知家長出於好心幫人，但係你地拎嘅係手足嘅錢（612、其他家長捐），可唔可以謹慎啲咁用呢？咁樣死攬個咩阿肥咩小車手，只會令手足們灰心，喺香港辛辛苦苦抗爭嘅成果就係比呢班自私撚移民，仲要一家大細過哂去。。<br />\n<br />\n我有時真係想知佢地做咗啲咩先需要走佬，香港大把人比人告暴動都未走而到個車手走？？ 唔係想搞分化但可唔可以有少少責任分清楚邊啲人先需要幫呢？咁樣對唔對得住香港啲手足 仲有還押緊犠牲緊自己自由嘅手足呢？<br />\n<br />\n最後屌你老母臭系乜撚小車手 有架車唔撚賣要乞錢仲要人地比錢你運架車過去 仲有咁都肯幫佢嘅家長係咪食撚咗屎？對唔對得住喺香港冇地方住冇飯開嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完隔離個咩小車手澄清真係嬲到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10288be41b97af96056f1b46c9649ca3cd5f473d","tid":1943852,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"推到比班家長見到"},{"pid":"ccf9319972d28efb112ef54e36ed7daa2334c9f0","tid":1943852,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe89ab653f74c9248f4e146beb5e255e51b7e038","tid":1943852,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aea62d56065a82e6d9d2d17b508ce234266dcda6","tid":1943852,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"e02204358184e4805ebe27a18f00b6690ac92c1d","tid":1943852,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7fe0de3f9abf400417b9e6ef2db0406f1ce2ed6d","ti